│ ### 1. Understanding the Issue                                                          │
│                                                                                         │
│ The `ipsccp` pass incorrectly deduces that an `alloca` instruction can have a constant  │
│ pointer value. In the provided reproducer, the pass analyzes a conditional branch: `br  │
